ponse to deutetrabenazine should be monitored more closely whenever a strong CYP450 2D6 inhibitor (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/84422/', '', 'Dalfampridine, Inotersen, Riluzole, Tafamidis', '', 1767369485);
