o deutetrabenazine should be monitored more closely whenever a strong CYP450 2D6 inhibitor (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/84466/', '', 'Levomilnacipran, Oxitriptan, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Tryptophan, Vilazodone', 'Dalfampridine, Tafamidis, Riluzole', 1767369485);
